text: Jordan Matthews (Born July 14, 2002) is an American soccer player who plays for the South Carolina Gamecocks in the NCAA Division I. == Club career == On July 24, 2019, Matthews appeared for Atlanta United 2, the USL Championship affiliate of Atlanta United FC, starting in a 2–2 draw with Charlotte Independence. == References == ==External links== * Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:American soccer players Category:Association football defenders Category:Atlanta United 2 players Category:Soccer players from Georgia (U.S. state) Category:USL Championship players
